{"tid":1214009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(了解你既對手）畜聾隊應該係呢D人","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:34:57.000Z","uid":2383,"like":116,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"54c096186fe9e0fbb05518eff0b165e5e0d69a23","tid":1214009,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"盧偉聰講既戴晒面罩就係唔想俾人認出既暴徒係咪佢地：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gc10gcu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgc10gcu.png&h=67892354&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnVPTZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnVPTZd.png&h=038c5948&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa6SRLV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa6SRLV.png&h=2d49f024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該分別係裝備齊全 比一般警察fit少少既<br />\n鐵路反應隊 編制34人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fowjwMj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfowjwMj.png&h=ed751737&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p4Vz46r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4Vz46r.png&h=18017056&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQvsFEO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQvsFEO.png&h=ac95d4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反恐特勤隊 約141人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vkTU46G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvkTU46G.png&h=fa4b6133&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GehirH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GehirH.png&h=be64e115&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqTByZ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgqTByZ7.png&h=7520c2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWG3YrR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWG3YrR.png&h=9c85f0a